{
  "texts": [
    "Data extraction algorithm OMIM APIOMIM provides API endpoints to access its data.",
    "We obtained an API key and used the API to access OMIM gene and phenotype descriptions.",
    "We will refer to these descriptions as \"OMIM texts\" to make it easy to explain.",
    "We made API calls to programmatically retrieve OMIM texts on December 16 th, 2022.",
    "OMIM API allows 250 API requests per day per API key."
  ]
}